title: At Last, At Last, La Moglie Vergine, The Virgin Wife 1975

sources.title: At Last At Last La Moglie Vergine The Virgin Wife
sources.description: When newlywed Valentina returns from her honeymoon still a virgin, and her young but impotent husband Giovannino seems helpless, a solution must be found to remedy the embarrassing situation. Edwige Fenech plays the distraught wife whose husband has to have sex with Carroll Baker before he can fulfill his marital duties.   Italian with Optional English Subtitles
